üí° What is Python?
Python is an open-source, high-level, and object-oriented programming language created by Guido van Rossum. 
It has an extensive ecosystem with vast libraries and frameworks like Django, Flask, TensorFlow, and Pandas, making it powerful for multiple use cases!




